<!doctype html>
<html lang="pt-BR">
<head>
  <meta charset="utf-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1"/>
  <title>Confirmar no WhatsApp</title>
  <style>
    body{
      margin:0;
      font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
      background:#0b0b0b;
      color:#fff;
      display:flex;
      align-items:center;
      justify-content:center;
      min-height:100vh;
      padding:18px;
    }
    .box{
      width:560px;
      max-width:100%;
      background:#111;
      border:1px solid #222;
      border-radius:18px;
      padding:18px;
      box-shadow:0 14px 40px rgba(0,0,0,.55);
    }
    h1{margin:0 0 8px; font-size:22px;}
    .ok{color:#c9a227; font-weight:900;}
    .sub{
      color:#cfcfcf;
      margin:0 0 14px;
      font-weight:700;
      line-height:1.4;
    }
    .card{
      margin-top:12px;
      background:#0f0f0f;
      border:1px solid #222;
      border-radius:14px;
      padding:12px;
      color:#eaeaea;
      font-weight:700;
      font-size:14px;
    }
    .row{
      display:flex;
      justify-content:space-between;
      gap:10px;
      padding:6px 0;
      border-bottom:1px solid #1f1f1f;
    }
    .row:last-child{border-bottom:none;}
    .k{color:#bdbdbd;}
    .btns{
      display:flex;
      gap:10px;
      margin-top:14px;
      flex-wrap:wrap;
    }
    a{
      display:inline-block;
      text-decoration:none;
      padding:12px 14px;
      border-radius:14px;
      border:1px solid #333;
      color:#111;
      font-weight:900;
      background:#c9a227;
      cursor:pointer;
      flex:1;
      text-align:center;
      min-width:220px;
    }
    a.secondary{
      background:#151515;
      color:#fff;
      border:1px solid #2a2a2a;
      font-weight:900;
    }
    .hint{
      margin-top:12px;
      color:#bdbdbd;
      font-size:12px;
      font-weight:700;
      line-height:1.4;
      white-space: pre-line;
    }
    code{
      display:block;
      margin-top:8px;
      padding:10px;
      border-radius:12px;
      background:#0c0c0c;
      border:1px solid #222;
      color:#ddd;
      font-size:12px;
      overflow:auto;
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="box">
    <h1 class="ok">✅ Só falta confirmar no WhatsApp</h1>

    <p class="sub">
      Seu horário foi criado como <b>pendente</b>.
      Agora confirme enviando a mensagem para o WhatsApp oficial da barbearia (<b><%= barbershopWppDisplay %></b>)
      e clicando no link de confirmação.
      <br/>Esse link expira em <b>30 minutos</b>.
    </p>

    <div class="card">
      <div class="row"><span class="k">Barbeiro</span><span><%= barberName %></span></div>
      <div class="row"><span class="k">Cliente</span><span><%= nome %></span></div>
      <div class="row"><span class="k">Telefone</span><span><%= telefone %></span></div>
      <div class="row"><span class="k">Data</span><span><%= data %></span></div>
      <div class="row"><span class="k">Horário</span><span><%= horario %></span></div>
      <div class="row"><span class="k">Status</span><span>agendado (pendente)</span></div>
    </div>

    <div class="btns">
      <a href="<%= waLink %>">Abrir WhatsApp da barbearia</a>
    </div>

    <div class="hint">
Como confirmar:
1) Clique em "Abrir WhatsApp da barbearia"
2) Envie a mensagem
3) No WhatsApp, clique no link "Confirmar" que veio na mensagem

    </div>
  </div>
</body>
</html>